This project is designed to determine the difficulty of the English language using subtitles.  The titles of the films and their scores are taken from https://puzzle-movies.com. 

A reference to the raw data: https://disk.yandex.ru/d/j8Uv_FEyszzEPA
A reference to the interim data: https://disk.yandex.ru/d/GLRu4kczRVWtVg

if you want work start this project on you computer, you need use poetry for install environment and dvc for start pipline. 

The data is not pre-processed in notebook, but through pipline (src + dvc). If you want start pipline use 'dvc repro'.